               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa lǝdatu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of
                     ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” (fols. 3ra-4ra)
 - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     3ra-4ra) 
 II) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     4ra-90rb)
 III) Maṣḥafa fǝlsatu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the
                     Translation of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” (fols. 90va-96rb)
 IV) Taʾammǝra Takla
                     Hāymānot “Miracles of Takla Haymanot”: 19 miracles (fols. 97ra-105va)
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
